data.description: Welcome to the market this "perfectly" charming 3 bedroom 2 bath in desireable Green and White neighborhood of Matawan.  Perfect for starter home! Perfect for downsizing! Perfect for everthing in between!  Kitchen is perfectly appointed with warm maple cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ceramic tile floors.  TV and Dining room are perfectly accomodating with ample space, vaulted ceilings, and recessed lighting.  Perfect for entertaining in the private, fenced in, park-like yard.  Perfetly situated in town for access to local amenities and transportation options.  Come see if it is the "perfect" place for you!
